      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you lean even more into his specific observations about the people themselves? Like, have him describe the contrast between their \"uncivilized\" way of life and the \"superior\" structure of European society. He should sound like he truly believes they are incapable of self-governance.",
